<div id="home">
  <div id="intro">
    <p><strong>Sonnax</strong> is a diversified supplier of <em>specialized drivetrain products</em> to the automotive and commercial vehicle industries, and to industrial sectors utilizing drivetrain technology.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="col-1" class="group">
    <div id="parts">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h3><%= link_to 'Transmission Parts', transmission_path %></h3>
          <%= link_to(image_tag('ts-parts.jpg', :alt => 'Transmission Parts'), transmission_path) %>
          <p>Sonnax transmission parts are known in the automatic transmission repair industry for effectively restoring full operation of automatic transmissions and salvaging expensive valve bodies. The Transmission product catalog has become the de facto industry instruction manual, guiding builders from transmission complaints to product solutions. Popular Sure Cure<sup>&reg;</sup> kits provide the key products to repair a particular unit.</p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h3><%= link_to 'Torque Converter Parts', torque_converter_path %></h3>
          <%= link_to(image_tag('tc-parts.jpg', :alt => 'Torque Converter Parts'), torque_converter_path) %>
          <p>Sonnax is the acknowledged global leader in the manufacture and distribution of torque converter components for standard and high performance converters. A full line of components ranges from precisely machined billet-steel converter covers to the smallest washer or O-ring. Torque converter remanufacturers worldwide confide in Sonnax to provide superior products, the highest level of customer service, and responsive technical support.</p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h3><%= link_to "High Performance Transmission Parts", high_performance_transmission_path %></h3>
          <%= link_to(image_tag('hp-parts.jpg', :alt => 'High Performance Parts'), high_performance_transmission_path) %>
          <p>Sonnax provides high performance components for automatic transmissions and torque converters for racing and other extreme service conditions. A full line of components for the Powerglide transmission, a longtime staple of performance racing, is complemented by a growing line of enhanced products for other popular heavy duty, performance applications. Sonnax also offers informed technical support to builders in selecting parts to fit their performance requirements.</p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <h3><%= link_to "Power Train Savers", power_train_savers_path %></h3>
          <%= link_to(image_tag('driveline-parts.jpg', :alt => 'Driveline Parts'), power_train_savers_path) %>
          <p>The Power Train Saver<sup>&reg;</sup> is a patented drivetrain protection device that mounts into your existing driveshaft. Once installed, this device prevents over-torque damage that can ruin differentials, gears, axles and driveshafts. In an over-torque situation, our precisely calibrated Torque Fuses<sup>&reg;</sup> shear before drivetrain damage occurs, while the unit design holds the driveshaft in place, saving costly repairs and downtime.</p>
        </li>

      </ul>
    </div>
